name: Pastel Sky
description:
Sometimes, I have a thought that it is hard to live a life, I want to disappear to somewhere
where no one cannot find me. I am too discouraged and desperate to handle things.
At the same time, I also have many things I want to do which I never thought I could do. I
love drawing and will always keep drawing until I get old. I want to grow up strong and try my
best in everyday life.
Pastel Sky work communicates about conflicts that arise in myself. Even if I am sad or fail at
something, I still have a bright sky with me.
